Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.12,0:02:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝是ChaosChoir的间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.40,0:02:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在一路同行期间萌发了对酷的爱恋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.17,0:02:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ChaosChoir连这份感情也要利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.29,0:02:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在遭遇到敌人时\N酷选择的同契对象不是菲萝而是蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.32,0:02:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散发光芒的宝石打磨修饰过后被人们所喜爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.80,0:02:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但散落在路上的\N脏石子被踩踏也好破损也好没人会在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同是石头的话成为宝石会更幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.24,0:02:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为幸福都流向明亮的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.52,0:02:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十二唱 拟煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.84,0:03:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 菲萝果然失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在预料之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来按计划进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.50,0:03:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 快点搭帐篷做晚上睡觉的准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.70,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都睡了那么久了 你还真能睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡足吃饱是我的特长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晕车所以很难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像酷一样反应迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么大声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.25,0:03:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头会晕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没礼貌的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.51,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话没事的蕾和菲萝看来都是反应迟钝喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.94,0:04:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.87,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.95,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道治晕车的药草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一会儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像任务失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那也是没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.76,0:04:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就明白这任务对你来说太艰巨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.71,0:04:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.64,0:04:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拟煌珠之身还想指望什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.17,0:04:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子的碎石子想挤进人和煌珠之中是绝对不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达给你最后的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死酷德·望·朱鲁爱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.81,0:04:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.95,0:05:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们目的实现之后你也就能成为真正的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦...苦...苦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良药苦口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦也得有个度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.26,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这是Enrica的果实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了这个能缓解些苦味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.73,0:05:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来感觉好多了 很清爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.19,0:05:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝还知道这么个有效的方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个看上去很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.73,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是毒性很强的毒草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.98,0:05:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃一粒种子身体就会发麻难以动弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要采那些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是因为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个埋在地下的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上睡觉的时候毒虫就不会爬过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝懂得还真多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然命令我杀死酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的事 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.08,0:06:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么愿意一辈子都做拟煌珠吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.54,0:06:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真正的核石的话谁也不会理你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.05,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核石...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不幸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.20,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想做个普通人却成了碎石子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.83,0:06:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要杀了酷你就能成为宝石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情我怎么下得了手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.10,0:06:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在他眼里你什么都不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我同契过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要你的时候利用一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.67,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使对拟煌珠的我他也像对待蕾一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有选择你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.07,0:07:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.59,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.01,0:07:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 只是碎石子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老掉牙了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.42,0:07:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要修理一下 请大家先休息休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我在等的时候摘些果子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.12,0:07:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到一个有很多Enrica果的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起跟着去 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要帮忙修车啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子一个人不危险吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.88,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里龙一个人总会搞定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.51,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.81,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.68,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗 酷 我扔喽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.74,0:08:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到很平静嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.58,0:08:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷和菲萝现在正两人世界哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有酷在旁边不会有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很相信他嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.57,0:08:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是...有所进展了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.00,0:08:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把他稍微借出一会儿也不要紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.76,0:08:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要让菲萝调节一下情绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 当然不是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.42,0:08:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少骗人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定是瞄准的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上都粘粘的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还粘着呢 脸颊上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 酷害羞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要当真好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.48,0:09:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.60,0:09:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得菲萝最近没什么精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你一点也不在意我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.46,0:09:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.20,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.37,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝 和我同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 酷 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 这个地方也有巢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.99,0:10:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 那样的东西出来了谁见了都会逃跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.32,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 酷没有逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.38,0:10:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我是男的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.51,0:10:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护女孩子是老大挂在嘴边的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要藏起来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是觉得很难为情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾是七煌宝树吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想成为七煌宝树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.49,0:11:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这使酷陷入险境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七煌宝树什么的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.25,0:11:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家尽情吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.93,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是久违的我做的料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也切了蔬菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.78,0:11:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没能帮上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 就当是消除压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的 给我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托冷静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.84,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.11,0:11:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷也是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.56,0:11:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷的事 不负责任地怂恿你反而让你受伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 菲萝真是个好女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.52,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然都是些古怪的家伙但都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也要多多帮助他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.78,0:12:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的 两个人在鬼鬼祟祟地说些什么 很可疑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.99,0:12:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.27,0:12:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.05,0:12:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.18,0:12:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会真的想就这样和大家在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.63,0:12:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为这种事会被原谅吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是碎石子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.48,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们之中没有你的容身之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找吃的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙威干劲十足的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.05,0:12:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会沾到油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想待在你的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 认真打磨的话无论什么都会变干净的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微用心了一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.02,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再有极品葡萄酒的话就完美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可只有泡乏了的咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.84,0:13:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝菲萝特制的鲜果汁如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.51,0:13:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我为弥补没做菜而做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么芳醇的香味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽的甘甜滑过喉咙回味无穷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.93,0:14:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.25,0:14:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝 给我也倒点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给酷的是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你倒上溶入我的爱意的特制白兰地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.73,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷 和我接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.55,0:14:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 你做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是来和你道别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.96,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道别？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里分手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.13,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样 等等 菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易相处融洽起来了 这是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是那样想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装温柔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是ChaosChoir的特工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我的使命就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死酷德·望·朱鲁爱特你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.77,0:15:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝也不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.93,0:15:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.79,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体动不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.58,0:15:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要杀了你 我就能成为真正的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成为真正的煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不和蕾同契就不能战斗了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能攻击菲萝你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反击啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.05,0:16:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.61,0:16:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗你的坏女孩正想杀了你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢我就别对我好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别同情碎石子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不和我战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.39,0:16:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么下得了手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们同契过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 菲萝是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时那么开朗但总觉得有点寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有精神但总觉得在怕着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.63,0:17:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但体贴又直爽这一点毫无疑问是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝不可能是坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.93,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再愤怒一些啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再恨我一些啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.68,0:17:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对我那么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了杀你别无选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.17,0:17:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌和我们在一起吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对碎石子来说太耀眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.61,0:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 叫你别再那么说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.61,0:17:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝就是菲萝 怎么会是碎石子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢作为同伴之一的菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢蕾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 “我喜欢蕾”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.79,0:18:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.18,0:18:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心喜欢蕾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要甩了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.53,0:18:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.47,0:18:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算告一段落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.92,0:18:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告一段落？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱七八糟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱七八糟的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算平静下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.76,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请就这样不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.04,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后会是什么下场我也是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.15,0:19:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊 就算是没用的石子分别时也会痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.94,0:19:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.88,0:19:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点啊 菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.83,0:20:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲萝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.41,0:20:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今只在煦春{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.39,0:20:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕手入梦{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却时间{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.36,0:20:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至永远{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颂词是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今只在煦春{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕手入梦{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却时间{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.75,0:20:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治愈之颂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微笑{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至永远{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.60,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假核石变成了真核石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在做梦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.03,0:20:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能和酷出色地战斗了
